body:
I literary ban this champ all the time now because it is so annoying to face.  I would say of the last 10 Xeraths I have faced  I am significantly confident only 1 was not using scripts.  It is very obvious in low elo...  The fact that this is an issue that to me is worth using my ban every time on is kinda ridiculous.

{{champion:101}} 
REWORK TIME.
